{"pageProps":{"post":{"_createdAt":"2022-06-17T05:33:18Z","_id":"d60def83-9bd4-4b5f-983e-d4e5f9040655","author":{"image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-339f8e320ddfad52225d31a181b162996e1c02d1-876x876-png","_type":"reference"}},"name":"ðŸ‘¾ Game Master"},"body":[{"_key":"9980f323429a","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"e1aa49be8aba0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"What is Cash Flow From Financing?"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h2"},{"_key":"3700da3cb64d","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"03bb2f2da3390","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"307567edafbe","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"31f07b1930dd","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Cash flow from financing implies the amount of cash the business raises from or spends on finance-related activities."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"fb6d9e21ed7e","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"25675fc4cd48","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"62fd73d37196","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"66e4844be8530","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"A typical example of cash flow from financing is dividends payment. Many companies are paying out dividends to their investors as a reward for their shareholders. Dividends can act as a useful strategy for a company to reward and attract investors."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"9a200b91d152","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"e5175ab2f9cd","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"c97c8836cd44","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"4201ee5191b30","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Another example of cash flow from financing is bond issuance. Many companies are issuing long-term bonds for investors to purchase. Both equities (i.e. stocks) and debt (i.e. bonds) are sources for a company to raise capital and increase their cash on hand."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"ef8ada75f4eb","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"85e78ef90ded","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"d1548d44b3f8","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"238dc716e6cd","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The picture below shows the cash flow from the financing activities of Nvidia. The spreadsheet includes data from the fiscal year 2019 to 2021."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"3f8697be5867","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"fc51e84fc442","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"99a7bc72ffb8","_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-2f59a10282814a64570cb5971a4172116b126f6e-1382x472-png","_type":"reference"}},{"_key":"d163eda482b0","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"907d11f0daed0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"}],"comments":[],"description":"A section in cash flow statement.","mainImage":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-b3252dd232d1e72c174a071a913421c52d78b289-900x500-jpg","_type":"reference"}},"slug":{"_type":"slug","current":"cash-flow-from-financing"},"title":"Cash Flow From Financing"}},"__N_SSG":true}